# Purpose: Keeps Docker build contexts small and private.
# Pipeline role: Prevents Docker image builds from copying local databases, private source data, node_modules, virtual environments, and Git metadata.
# Dependencies: Docker build context rules; should stay aligned with .gitignore when generated folders change.

.git
.venv
__pycache__
*.pyc
.DS_Store

data/private
data/sample statements
data/bronze
data/silver
data/gold
data/anonymized
warehouse

Frontend/node_modules
Frontend/dist
Frontend/.vite
